<template>
    <v-card>
      <!-- Search field at the beginning -->
      <v-text-field
        v-model="search"
        append-icon="mdi-magnify"
        label="Search"
        single-line
        hide-details
      ></v-text-field>

      <!-- Data table with "View" button -->

        :headers="headers"
        :items="desserts"

        class="elevation-1"

            <v-toolbar-title>Nutrition</v-toolbar-title>
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
